headline: TE Connectivity to Host 2025 Investor Day
summary: TE Connectivity (NYSE: TEL), a world leader in connectors and sensors, will host an Investor Day on November 20, 2025, in Philadelphia. Speakers will include Chief Executive Officer Terrence Curtin, Chief Financial Officer Heath Mitts, as well as other members of TE Connectivity's senior leadership team.
